gamble
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:A `spreader' (phs the more usual term of butchers and farmers) for keeping the hocks of hung carcases apart.
Origin: [none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain: [none]
Region: [none]
